{"tid":1843831,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人 How bad do you want it?","createTime":"2020-01-26T11:05:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-26T11:15:34.000Z","uid":27670,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"c51a4c95f7453e30cca5ca80d4717b20798d5eb8","tid":1843831,"uid":27670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T11:05:19.000Z","msg":"今次肺炎根本就係黃金機會 最佳助攻<br />\n俾所有人睇到中共港共係幾咁自私無能<br />\n而家就係我地統戰所有人既最好機會<br />\n藍絲支那人係咪忘本自私醜惡？絕對係<br />\n但係要推倒呢個政權 終有一日必然係需要佢地<br />\n點解中共咁叻玩分化？因為只要人民夠團結佢地就死撚硬<br />\n當年老毛咪一樣係統戰知識分子打國民黨<br />\n你估佢想咩？但係佢就係夠忍得<br />\n只要主線成功 之後要清算有幾難？<br />\n你地想攬住個光環輸 定係成為最後既贏家？<br />\n你地到底有幾想贏？<br />\nWhen you want to succeed as bad as you want to breathe, then you will be successful<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/wgAgriozwks\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FwgAgriozwks&d=1bJdDSIrk6tBa%2BBM68SGek6%2B9elrQwgXj79VqWXxFjk%3D&h=926a6018\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/wgAgriozwks</a>"},{"pid":"442c4c189d5c01bf4349ac3bce0aee477f4d3e81","tid":1843831,"uid":167705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T11:06:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/07Z2qYi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F07Z2qYi.jpg&h=2af6f9b0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7180e57681b4aae0c5df49b3126dbc0978f03583","tid":1843831,"uid":266011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T11:15:34.000Z","msg":"Agreed"}]}